data.description: Welcome to 904 Cherrydale Street! This stunning 3 bed, 2 bath home is perfect for anyone seeking comfort and space. With a large den, dining room, living room, and breakfast nook, this home is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet night in. The updated interior features a cozy fireplace and plenty of natural light, creating a warm atmosphere that's perfect for relaxing. With 1,974 sq ft of living space and a quarter-acre lot, this home offers plenty of room to spread out and enjoy the beautiful surroundings. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own a truly special home!
